snippet.title: Phenix Corrupta Trailer
snippet.description:
Phenix Corrupta is a game developed for MSX2.
It's free to play in a browser emulator or download it to play in your own emulator of choice or on real hardware!
Go check it out here: https://caspercroes.itch.io/phenix-corrupta
